      "id": "PopularPost263304",
      "post_content": "@Guest...: It was Black and not Red because the color pie changes as Wizards finds the correct places for mechanics and abilities; the same reason why [Prodigal Sorcerer](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Prodigal Sorcerer) got shifted to [Prodigal Pyromancer](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Prodigal Pyromancer). Note that land destruction is still in Black's color pie (see [Polluted Dead](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Polluted Dead), it just tends to be more powerful in Red.",
      "posted_by": "sarroth",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost263304\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl08_post\">@Guest...: It was Black and not Red because the color pie changes as Wizards finds the correct places for mechanics and abilities; the same reason why <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Prodigal Sorcerer\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Prodigal Sorcerer\">Prodigal Sorcerer</a> got shifted to <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Prodigal Pyromancer\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Prodigal Pyromancer\">Prodigal Pyromancer</a>. Note that land destruction is still in Black's color pie (see <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Polluted Dead\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Polluted Dead\">Polluted Dead</a>, it just tends to be more powerful in Red.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl08_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl08_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '263304'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy20957\">sarroth</span>\r\n                                (8/19/2012 5:11:46 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPo